name: Farmer Frank
description: Based Farmer Frank ($FRANK) is a farming protocol built on the $BASE blockchain. It allows users to earn rewards from other meme coins through a unique "farming" system. Users who buy and sell $FRANK gain "Farm Points." More Farm Points entitle users to a larger share of meme coin rewards accumulated through a community-chosen "farmed" meme coin. A buy and sell tax on $FRANK transactions is used to collectively purchase the chosen meme coin. $FRANK offers users the potential to earn rewards from multiple meme coins through a single holding, benefit from the potential price appreciation of $FRANK itself, and participate in a community-driven meme coin farming strategy.
